{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":173333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[32],"categories_output":[{"ID":32,"slug":"%e8%ae%be%e8%ae%a1%e6%b4%9e%e5%af%9f","name":"设计洞察","term_taxonomy_id":32,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":42}],"tags":[39,45,44,48],"tags_output":[{"ID":39,"slug":"%e7%bd%91%e9%a1%b5%e8%ae%be%e8%ae%a1","name":"网页设计","term_taxonomy_id":39,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":25},{"ID":45,"slug":"%e7%bd%91%e9%a1%b5%e9%85%8d%e8%89%b2","name":"网页配色","term_taxonomy_id":45,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":44,"slug":"%e8%89%b2%e5%bd%a9%e6%90%ad%e9%85%8d","name":"色彩搭配","term_taxonomy_id":44,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":3},{"ID":48,"slug":"%e9%bb%91%e8%89%b2","name":"黑色","term_taxonomy_id":48,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1}],"thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_fae18c58df3438f8272c9c52-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfaecdffccxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_fae18c58df3438f8272c9c52-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfaecdffccxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_fae18c58df3438f8272c9c52-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfaecdffccxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_full":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_fae18c58df3438f8272c9c52-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfaecdffccxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"date_day":"03","date_month":"06","date_month_e":"June","date_year":"2012","date_weekday":"Sunday","title":"网页设计中对黑色调的理解","excerpt":"黑色，是网页设计中常用的色彩，品牌网站等等，30%是运用了黑色为底色，浅谈下对黑色的理解","content":"<p>每隔一段时间我都要在网页设计的各个方面做一个研究探讨，以提升网页设计水平。</p>\n<p>黑色，是网页设计中常用的色彩，品牌网站等等，30%是运用了黑色为底色，浅谈下对黑色的理解，自己谈谈网页设计中对黑色的理解吧，嘿嘿，支持的投一票，有不对的地方希望指点喔～</p>\n<h4>从配色角度来说</h4>\n<p>黑白灰属于中性色，没有绝对的冷暖之意，很方便的能和其它色彩搭配而恰到好处，不偏激不冷淡</p>\n<h4>从网站需求来说</h4>\n<p>如果大多面对品牌产品，黑色容易和其他色彩产生对比，突出产品，彰显视觉冲击力，黑色使用适度不容易造成视觉疲劳，利于各种产品展示</p>\n<h4>从用户体验来说</h4>\n<p>黑色容易让用户挖掘到显眼信息，并有效指引用户操作行为。黑色用的不好会很深沉，阴暗，让网站没有活力，但是如果稍加搭配其他的色彩，比如蓝色，橘黄，红色，绿色，或者多彩搭配，都会给人跳出黑色的深沉感，给人活力，持续性的访问页面的心理。</p>\n<h4>从喜好方式来说</h4>\n<p>部分设计者，或者客户，偏爱深色搭配，使用深色，再加之配合其他色彩，如白色，能让网站大气简洁。很多企业站也是为了大气简洁，让用户易懂，突出视觉压力，喜好风格也是一方面</p>\n<h4>最后从创意艺术来说</h4>\n<p>黑色适合挖掘创意元素（比如把一个图形，乱七八糟分割成其他的图形，然后加之组合），很容易组成网页的创意元素并运用，不容易产生不协调特征，黑色容易进行创意元素的制作和灵感。</p>\n<p>嘿嘿，大概我能想到的就这么多，希望对自己也是个思考，对设计者能有所帮助</p>\n","slug":"web-design-black-color-understanding","prev":[{"ID":163333,"title":"网页设计怎样才算精通,浅谈感想","excerpt":"找工作写简历也好，巴拉巴拉推广产品拉客户也好，如何理解对某一个领域或者技术\"精通\"，到底精通是否存在，还是一个虚构的假设，或者是一个最终的目标？踏入职场后每个人都会在一些时间给自己贴上标签。这个标签怎么贴，也许还是需要一定的技术含量。","slug":"webdesign-proficient","post_date":"2012-06-02 01:31:03","post_date_gmt":"2012-06-02 01:31:03","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_2359ec44785b1d2aab0318aa-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecbdaabaaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_2359ec44785b1d2aab0318aa-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecbdaabaaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_2359ec44785b1d2aab0318aa-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecbdaabaaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":183333,"title":"怎么提高网页配色能力,总结学习方法","excerpt":"配色，在设计领域起着至关重要的作用，也是很难的一项基本功，在此，自己总结了自己的学习方法。","slug":"webdesign-color-learning-method-summary","post_date":"2012-06-04 16:52:08","post_date_gmt":"2012-06-04 16:52:08","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_82c94a56e9ca8db3d3472696-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcaecadbdxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_82c94a56e9ca8db3d3472696-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcaecadbdxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true]